name: 1° Gems - Ginesse with Dolomite
description:
A beautiful Ginesse rock with some rare Dolomite gems.

This type of stone can be found in the desert to the south, just beyond the Tezzardz lands.


I'm grateful for the help of all the astute collectors in this metaverse who are helping me recover my lost collection with all my 250 rare pieces of gems.

 I moved these days to Twitter, there I live as Mr.Walkscapes.tez

All collectors who retrieve some of my 250 precious gems will participate in exclusive giveaways, raffles, and will have exclusive access to some of my treasures once I return to H = N. 

Thanks a lot
